HEADWORD: Unallied
<hw>Un`al*lied"</hw> <pr>(⟦ucr⟧n`⟦acr⟧l*l⟦imac⟧d")</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<def>Not allied; having no ally; having no connection or relation;
